message.content: ∀ {f : ℝ → ℝ} {a b : ℝ}, a < b → 2 ≤ b - a → (∀ x ∈ Icc a b, |f x| ≤ 1) → (∀ x ∈ Icc a b, |f'' x| ≤ 1) → ∀ x ∈ Icc a b, |f' x| ≤ 2

∀ {f : ℝ → ℝ} {a b : ℝ},
  2 ≤ b - a →
    (∀ x ∈ Icc a b, |f x| ≤ 1) →
      (∀ x ∈ Icc a b, HasDerivWithinAt f (f' x) (Icc a b) x) →
        (∀ x ∈ Icc a b, HasDerivWithinAt f' (f'' x) (Icc a b) x) →
          (∀ x ∈ Icc a b, |f'' x| ≤ 1) → ∀ x ∈ Icc a b, |f' x| ≤ 2

∀ {f : ℝ → ℝ} {a b : ℝ},
  a < b → 2 ≤ b - a →
    (∀ x ∈ Icc a b, |f x| ≤ 1) →
      (∀ x ∈ Icc a b, |iterated_deriv 2 f x| ≤ 1) →
        ∀ x ∈ Icc a b, |deriv f x| ≤ 2

∀ {f : ℝ → ℝ} {a b : ℝ},
  2 ≤ b - a →
    (∀ x ∈ Icc a b, |f x| ≤ 1) →
      (∀ x ∈ Icc a b, HasDerivAt f (deriv f x) x ∧ HasDerivAt (deriv f) (deriv (deriv f) x) x ∧ |deriv (deriv f) x| ≤ 1) →
        ∀ x ∈ Icc a b, |deriv f x| ≤ 2

∀ {f : ℝ → ℝ} {a b : ℝ},
  2 ≤ b - a →
    (∀ x ∈ Icc a b, |f x| ≤ 1) →
      (∀ x ∈ Icc a b, |f'' x| ≤ 1) → ∀ x ∈ Icc a b, |f' x| ≤ 2

∀ {f : ℝ → ℝ} {a b : ℝ},
  2 ≤ b - a →
    (∀ x ∈ Icc a b, |f x| ≤ 1) →
      (∀ x ∈ Icc a b, ‖derivWithin (derivWithin f (Icc a b)) (Icc a b) x‖ ≤ 1) →
        ∀ x ∈ Icc a b, ‖derivWithin f (Icc a b) x‖ ≤ 2

∀ {f : ℝ → ℝ} {a b : ℝ},
  2 ≤ b - a →
    (∀ x ∈ Set.Icc a b, |f x| ≤ 1) →
      (∀ x ∈ Set.Icc a b, |f'' x| ≤ 1) → ∀ x ∈ Set.Icc a b, |f' x| ≤ 2

∀ {f : ℝ → ℝ} {a b : ℝ},
  2 ≤ b - a →
    (∀ x ∈ Set.Icc a b, |f x| ≤ 1) →
      (∀ x ∈ Set.Icc a b, HasDerivAt f (f' x) x) →
        (∀ x ∈ Set.Icc a b, HasDerivAt (f' x) (f'' x) x) →
          (∀ x ∈ Set.Icc a b, |f'' x| ≤ 1) →
            ∀ x ∈ Set.Icc a b, |f' x| ≤ 2
